<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>अमृतम</title>
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		.navbar-nav {
			margin: auto; /* Centers the navigation */
		}

		.nav-link {
			color: white;
		}

		.navbar-brand {
			font-weight: bold;
			font-size: large;
			color: white;
			font-size: 30px;
		}

		.hed {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: white;
		}

		.txt {
			color: black;
		}

		* {
			box-sizing: border-box;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
		}

		.containernew {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 20px;
			padding: 20px;
		}

		.cardnew {
			display: flex;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 800px;
			border: 1px solid #ddd;
			border-radius: 8px;
			overflow: hidden;
			background: #fff;
			box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

			.cardnew img {
				width: 50%;
				height: auto;
			}

			.cardnew .text {
				width: 50%;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
			}

		@@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.cardnew {
				flex-direction: column;
			}

				.cardnew img, .cardnew .text {
					width: 100%;
				}
		}


		.product-card {
			background: #fff;
			border-radius: 10px;
			padding: 15px;
			text-align: center;
			box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		}

			.product-card:hover {
				box-shadow: 0 10px 20px #00AEEF;
				border-color: #00AEEF;
			}

		.sale-badge {
			background-color: red;
			color: white;
			font-size: 14px;
			padding: 5px 10px;
			border-radius: 5px;
			position: absolute;
			top: 10px;
			left: 10px;
		}

		.price {
			color: #999;
			text-decoration: line-through;
		}

		.discounted-price {
			font-size: 20px;
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.rating {
			color: gold;
		}

		.product-img {
			max-width: 100%;
			border-radius: 5px;
			height: 230px;
		}

		.btn-custom {
			background-color: #29ABE2;
			color: white;
			border-radius: 5px;
			padding: 10px;
			font-size: 16px;
			width: 100%;
			transition: 0.3s;
		}

			.btn-custom:hover {
				background-color: #1C8CC4;
			}

		.contact-container {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			text-align: center;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 600px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		h2 {
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
			width: 100%;
			padding: 10px;
			margin: 10px 0;
			border: 1px solid #ccc;
			border-radius: 5px;
		}

		.contact-form button {
			width: 100%;
			padding: 10px;
			background: #00AEEF;
			color: white;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
			cursor: pointer;
		}

			.contact-form button:hover {
				background: #00AEEF;
			}

		@@media (max-width: 500px) {
			.contact-container {
				width: 90%;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg sticky-top" style="background-color: #00AEEF;">
		<div class="container">
			<!-- Left Logo -->
			<a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
				अमृतम
			</a>

			<!-- Navbar Toggler -->
			<button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
				<span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
			</button>

			<!-- Centered Navigation Links -->
			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
				<ul class="navbar-nav text-center">
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link active" href="#home">Home</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="#about">About</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="#product">Product</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<section id="home" style="width: 100vw; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden;">
		<img src="/Picture/gir cow.png" alt="Gir Cow Image"
			 style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
	</section>

	<section id="about">

		<div class="card text-center" style="background-color:#00AEEF;">
			<div class="card-body">
				<h5 class="card-title hed">Welcome to अमृतम</h5>
				<p class="card-text txt">
					A sanctuary of tradition, purity, and wellness. Our commitment to crafting exceptional A2 Gir Cow Ghee
					is matched only by our dedication to ethical and sustainable practices. Allow us to take you on a journey
					that celebrates our story, mission, values, and the remarkable team behind the brand.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="containernew">
			<div class="cardnew">
				<img src="/Picture/1.png" alt="Image 1">
				<div class="text">
					<p>
						<span style="font-size:20px"><b>Our Story - </b></span>
						Amrutam's roots trace back to a profound respect for time-honored dairy practices. A spark of inspiration ignited our founders' desire to share these invaluable benefits with a wider audience. Thus, Gaayam was born, a haven where the qualities of A2 Gir Cow Ghee and the significance of Gir cows merge seamlessly.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="cardnew" style="flex-direction: row-reverse;">
				<img src="/Picture/2.png" alt="Image 2">
				<div class="text">
					<p>
						<span style="font-size:20px"><b>Our Mission and Values - </b></span>
						At Amrutam, our mission is clear: to provide you with the purest A2 Gir Cow Ghee while preserving the essence of traditional dairy practices. Our values are the pillars that guide us: authenticity, quality, tradition, health, sustainability, and community engagement. Every step we take is rooted in these principles, ensuring that the products you experience embody the finest standards and cherished heritage.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="cardnew">
				<img src="/Picture/3.png" alt="Image 3">
				<div class="text">
					<p>
						<span style="font-size:20px"><b>Our Vision for the Future - </b></span>
						Our vision extends far beyond the present. Amrutam aspires to grow, innovate, and make a positive impact on both your well-being and the world around you. We envision expanding our offerings, igniting educational initiatives, and fostering community connections. Together, we're creating a legacy that celebrates tradition while embracing the possibilities of the future.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</section>

	<section id="product">
		<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center min-vh-100" style="background-color:#00AEEF;">
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<div class="product-card position-relative">
					<div class="sale-badge">Sale</div>
					<img src="/Picture/Ghee.png" alt="Product Image" class="product-img">
					<h5 class="mt-3">Gaayam A2 Gir Cow Ghee</h5>
					<div class="rating">
						⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ <span class="fw-bold text-dark">4.8</span> (56)
					</div>
					<p><span class="price">Rs. 1,299.00</span> <span class="discounted-price">Rs. 1,050.00</span></p>
					<button class="btn btn-custom">Buy</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<br />
	<br />

	<section id="contact">
		<div class="contact-container">
			<h2>Contact Us</h2>
			<form class="contact-form">
				<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
				<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
				<input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Subject" required>
				<textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
				<button type="submit">Send Message</button>
			</form>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div style="margin-top:20px">
		<div class="" style="background-color: #00AEEF;">
			<footer class="text-center text-lg-start text-white">
				<div class="container p-4">
					<div class="row my-2 align-items-center">
						<!-- Logo Section -->
						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-12 mb-4">
							<div class="rounded-circle bg-white shadow-1-strong d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
								<img src="/Picture/Amritam_Logo_New.jpg.png" height="180" alt="Amrutam Logo" loading="lazy" />
							</div>
						</div>

						<!-- Empty Columns (Can be removed or used) -->
						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-12 mb-4"></div>
						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-12 mb-4"></div>

						<!-- Contact Section -->
						<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-12 mb-2">
							<h5 class="text-uppercase mb-3">Contact</h5>
							<ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
								<li><p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt pe-2"></i> Warsaw, 57 Street, Poland</p></li>
								<li><p><i class="fas fa-phone pe-2"></i> +01 234 567 89</p></li>
								<li><p><i class="fas fa-envelope pe-2 mb-0"></i> contact@example.com</p></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Copyright Section -->
				<div class="text-center p-2 pb-2" style="background-color: #00AEEF;">
					© 2025 Copyright:
					<a class="text-white" href="/home">Amrutam</a>
				</div>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script>
		document.querySelectorAll('nav a').forEach(anchor => {
			anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
				e.preventDefault();
				document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
					behavior: 'smooth'
				});
			});
		});
	</script>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
